Class Account

java.lang.Object
src.models.Account
All Implemented Interfaces:
AccountVerifiable, TransactionLoggable
Direct Known Subclasses:
BankAccount, CheckingAccount, CreditCardAccount, InvestmentAccount
public abstract class Account extends Object implements AccountVerifiable, TransactionLoggable
Abstract base class for all account types. This class implements the AccountVerifiable and TransactionLoggable interfaces.
